HEADWORD: Clunch
<hw>Clunch</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Perh. fr.
<ets>clinch</ets> to make fast]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld>
